    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>WARNING: This game contains flashing images. If you are sensitive to flashing lights, please proceed with caution.</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Bear Ridge Summer Camp</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Jenny, a recent high school graduate navigating her first job as a camp counselor. Shy, a little awkward, but a gifted musician, she’s ready to break out of her shell, make new friends, and discover love. Help Jenny confront her insecurities, embrace her talents, and transform into the confident person she’s always dreamed of becoming. Will you guide her journey to self-discovery?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/e36a01924031255839a74d53500c89c5.poster.avif?t=1757455205\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/e36a01924031255839a74d53500c89c5.webm?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/e36a01924031255839a74d53500c89c5.mp4?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unravel the Chilling Truth </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in <strong><i>Bad Summer</i></strong>, a haunting visual novel experience that will pull you into a dark, eerie world. Do not expect a happy ending here. Play detective with unique phone call mini-games. Use your intuition to separate the humans from the horrors lurking within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/b98987fb54abb36cee81191eb66d59e4.poster.avif?t=1757455205\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/b98987fb54abb36cee81191eb66d59e4.webm?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/b98987fb54abb36cee81191eb66d59e4.mp4?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World of Terror Awaits </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brace yourself for pulse-pounding jump scares, unsettling analog horror sequences, and captivating storytelling, fully voiced in specific sections. Nothing is as it seems in Bad Summer. Your eyes will often deceive you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/d5406e2630213fb6798dfb7dd83a741f.poster.avif?t=1757455205\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/d5406e2630213fb6798dfb7dd83a741f.webm?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/d5406e2630213fb6798dfb7dd83a741f.mp4?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choices with Consequences</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every decision matters.</strong>  Can you save yourself? Save your friends? Are you willing to make sacrifices? Or would you rather play it safe? Shape your destiny and unlock the hidden secrets of <i>Bad Summer's</i> branching narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/53874c5b67bc611246088b3eefe29959.poster.avif?t=1757455205\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/53874c5b67bc611246088b3eefe29959.webm?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/53874c5b67bc611246088b3eefe29959.mp4?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Romance the Unknown </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge bonds with four unique romanceable characters, each brought to life with vibrant expressions and captivating movements. Into the brooding bad boys? How about bubbly, fun-spirited optimists? We have it all here. <br><br>The relationship you choose to pursue isn't a side quest. It'll directly affect your story in significant ways. <strong>Choose your love interest wisely.</strong> When all hope is lost, they'll protect you...or hinder you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/be51f4c433d09b04e237cfab97b17aa5.avif?t=1757455205\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras_big/be51f4c433d09b04e237cfab97b17aa5.avif?t=1757455205 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Replayability Redefined </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 20 achievements to unlock and multiple endings to discover, <i>Bad Summer</i> is an experience you'll revisit time and again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/f7d5ff0efff1ef022bc0a5cf84c3bf00.poster.avif?t=1757455205\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/f7d5ff0efff1ef022bc0a5cf84c3bf00.webm?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318500/extras/f7d5ff0efff1ef022bc0a5cf84c3bf00.mp4?t=1757455205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
